<p><a name="Critical" id="Critical"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Edward_Said&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Critical">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Critical</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.campus-watch.org/article/id/805" class="external text" title="http://www.campus-watch.org/article/id/805" rel="nofollow"><i>Edward Said</i></a> article by <a href="/wiki/David_Frum" title="David Frum">David Frum</a> published in <a href="/wiki/National_Review" title="National Review">National Review</a>, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2003-09-29"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="09-29"><a href="/wiki/September_29" title="September 29">September 29</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2003" title="2003">2003</a></span>, re-posted on <a href="/wiki/Campus_Watch" title="Campus Watch">Campus Watch</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.butterfliesandwheels.com/articleprint.php?num=23" class="external text" title="http://www.butterfliesandwheels.com/articleprint.php?num=23" rel="nofollow"><i>Debunking Edward Said</i></a> criticism of <i>Orientalism</i> by <a href="/wiki/Ibn_Warraq" title="Ibn Warraq">Ibn Warraq</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.geocities.com/martinkramerorg/SaidSplash.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.geocities.com/martinkramerorg/SaidSplash.htm" rel="nofollow">Edward Said's Splash</a> Said's impact on Middle Eastern studies, by <a href="/wiki/Martin_Kramer" title="Martin Kramer">Martin Kramer</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.camera.org/index.asp?x_context=8&amp;x_nameinnews=118&amp;x_article=198" class="external text" title="http://www.camera.org/index.asp?x_context=8&amp;x_nameinnews=118&amp;x_article=198" rel="nofollow">"Edward Said's Documented Deceptions"</a> by pro-Israel group <a href="/wiki/CAMERA" title="CAMERA" class="mw-redirect">CAMERA</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.brucebawer.com/said.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.brucebawer.com/said.htm" rel="nofollow">Edward W. Said, intellectual</a> by <a href="/wiki/Bruce_Bawer" title="Bruce Bawer">Bruce Bawer</a>, <a href="/wiki/The_Hudson_Review" title="The Hudson Review">The Hudson Review</a>, Winter 2002</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mywire.com/pubs/TheAtlantic/2003/09/01/377243/print/" class="external text" title="http://www.mywire.com/pubs/TheAtlantic/2003/09/01/377243/print/" rel="nofollow">Where the Twain Should Have Met</a> by <a href="/wiki/Christopher_Hitchens" title="Christopher Hitchens">Christopher Hitchens</a>, <a href="/wiki/The_Atlantic_Monthly" title="The Atlantic Monthly" class="mw-redirect">The Atlantic Monthly</a>, September 2003 (theatlantic.com <a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/doc/prem/200309/hitchens" class="external text" title="http://www.theatlantic.com/doc/prem/200309/hitchens" rel="nofollow">subscriber excerpt</a>)</li>
</ul>
